Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:41.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100830,101880}What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:43.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102480,103970}Try harder!
