Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108810,110020}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:51.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110840,111890}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113810,115190}Ah… ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115360,116690}- Ah…!\N- Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121650,123970}Lassie went too far…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148710,150150}What's up, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150770,151510}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152810,155000}Is it our guest while I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157440,158080}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158220,159200}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159550,161690}Is this the big dog yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:42.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161850,162910}That's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163140,164270}What about you Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166330,169970}The road was divided into four\Ndirections, and while I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170000,171310}I was sleepy and I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:51.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171340,171970}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177900,178850}And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179020,181220}We have guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181590,182570}Guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182660,185070}We are not guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185950,187510}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187640,188720}Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191300,192860}Very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192940,194120}Doucho is very sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:16.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194120,196220}his chest is almost bursting with pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196350,199980}So one of you will come and ease his grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209820,210810}Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216350,217580}Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219320,220270}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227210,229420}This is my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229900,232230}This is my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233220,236030}His name is Pace! His specialty\Nis moving the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236920,238630}I'm Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238970,241600}By the way, do you know\Na delicious bakery in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241700,243480}Bakery? Maybe that is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243650,246250}I know, Uncle Rice's bakery is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:06.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246300,246890}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246990,247890}That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247960,249320}He's helped by his daughter, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249340,250990}It's the best in the whole village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251110,252320}Well I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252460,254230}I have a place to go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254430,255430}Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:24.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263710,264930}We have finally finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264950,266670}Well, let's go for a walk\Nand have a drink together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270980,273310}Oh? Do you still deliver goods at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273390,275610}You work harder than we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279630,280410}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287670,289060}John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289390,291460}And Lassie? What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309530,311500}Lassie, isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311500,313040}Can you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322270,323370}And now, next…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323980,326600}We need some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:27.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326940,327920}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328350,329190}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329270,331420}This gentle miss, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333150,334130}Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334230,336830}Would your husband be reluctant to look at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336930,338180}I'm rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341290,342450}Stay there and hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344200,345090}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345260,346460}This is the best place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346620,347790}Come on, Doucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:00.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356520,360040}Ladies and gentlemen, this is\Nthe great partner of the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360160,362280}And this gentle miss,\NI hope you applaud them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365700,366810}And now, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366810,368900}you have the honor to see some of my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369090,371920}We have utensils and all kinds of pans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372220,373770}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379110,380740}Good! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381750,383320}You're welcome, thank you for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383450,385170}I want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385270,388800}Rory is doing business and\Nis traveling around England!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388880,390680}Me too I wish I would go to many places!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390710,391250}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391280,393110}My God! My God! My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393220,395380}I would forget something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395490,397000}Please buy me bread to eat at dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397030,398450}Okay! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400190,401490}Let's go! To the bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401520,403230}You are! You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403780,406340}How can you leave your job like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409280,410450}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410530,412320}Today there is no bread because all were sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412340,414270}- Not even one?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414780,417730}I'll bake a new batch tomorrow morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417880,419750}I understood, there is none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419830,421230}Don't you have bread for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421390,422130}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422220,424280}It's not for me, it is for Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424310,425370}Rory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425520,427970}Yes, that man who has a dog\Nwhich does amazing movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428060,430460}His voice is so loud that\NI can hear him from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430570,434210}He came to this village because I told\Nhim that we have a delicious bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:14.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434330,434970}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435000,435750}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435750,437150}We don't have anything to sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437150,438540}Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438540,439280}Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439620,442510}But will that man stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:23.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442740,443650}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443710,446720}Tomorrow morning I'll give you fresh bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:27.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446740,447300}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449820,450720}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450830,452620}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452880,456880}Fresh bread makes the hearts of people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457340,459510}Next to that beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459690,462080}Well, I will work tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462200,463590}But what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463690,465300}You have no house here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465790,468840}Nothing like that, I don't have\Na house at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469110,471330}So, will you sleep in the stable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471450,473380}No no, but I'm a vagabond!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473530,475040}Displacement is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475150,477080}Under the stars of the sky that seem to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477500,480080}Towards that sky to the large galaxies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480190,481910}I sleep under it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482100,483280}Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484920,486440}Sky and stars…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494580,496340}Look like they really fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496460,498210}Somehow this is scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498440,499090}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500240,502760}Have you traveled in many places?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502880,503830}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504440,506130}Just, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:32.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507660,512610}Manchester, Glasgow, Newcastle,\Nand also Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513220,514200}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514530,518100}I only went to the simple villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:43.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519950,523000}My father was like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523900,526480}I was used to staying out at night\Nand homeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:51.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526650,531380}but there are many people who are bored\Nto stay between the walls of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532330,536500}Yet within this dimly lit window is a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:02.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537320,542480}Thinking about it, this is warm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542890,545340}It seems that staying in a home\Nis a lot more better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:10.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546260,550890}But Uncle Rice is always angry\Nand screaming loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551580,552710}It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552840,554510}You should not say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554670,555870}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558940,559670}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560730,561940}It's Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569190,571660}Can't you smell the delicious things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579930,582220}Pace, it's delicious! It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582910,584260}Oh really? Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584460,586410}Oh really! Really really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586990,589680}But there is a problem with\Nthe handle of this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590850,593190}It can be used again after\Nit has been well repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593980,597350}It seems that Sandy's mother is interested\Nin keeping the dishes well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597430,598100}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598170,599940}This pot is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:00.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599970,600570}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600630,603020}I got it from my deceased grandmother\Nwhen I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603140,604710}That's why I cared about it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605150,608310}Is it you who made this tasty soup…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608580,609600}I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610560,612950}Is that right? I apologize for my insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613090,615960}Finally I knew! Isn't it, Duocho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619990,621720}What now are natural people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621780,623980}Haven't you seen a falling star\Nor something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624430,625190}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:26.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626260,626940}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627540,628660}It's a falling star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628850,630850}Eh? Where? Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630940,632230}Just gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632230,633390}I saw it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633470,636930}I really saw it! That is the devil… I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:44.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644230,644910}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645720,648150}They made a fire in such a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648240,650890}What if a fire starts because of that? Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651820,653930}Now, kids, have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:54.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653950,654620}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654680,656030}Although we enjoy being with you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656480,660170}Don't you have mothers and\Na warm home waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660590,662900}Children have specific times\Nand can't go out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:05.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662990,665310}You are not like me, homeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665780,667110}See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667250,669070}Did you have amazing\Nthings for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671990,674230}Doucho wants to make this happen\Nwith greater success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674880,676420}- Bye!\N- Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:16.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676440,676920}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677250,678800}Lassie, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681860,685330}That boy owns a huge dog,\Nbeautiful shape, Doucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:26.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686280,686990}It was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707230,708580}I have finished, Doucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708710,709890}Should I sleep now?
Comment: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:58.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:718113,718113}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:44.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763770,764910}That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:52.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771150,772740}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774370,775530}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775700,777370}It's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777400,779190}Hey! It's a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779350,781000}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783780,785720}Oh? A fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786000,787850}It's near my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:08.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788310,788990}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789260,791760}Water! Water! Curse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795500,796420}Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806910,808050}It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:34.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814090,814960}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:37.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816930,817830}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817970,819850}I came to deliver the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820180,821290}Hello, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821410,823410}What? Have you brought milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824020,825210}Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825330,827130}it's not from my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:51.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827210,831030}Listen, Mr. Rory needs milk with\Nthe bread at breakfast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831060,832240}Ah, that 's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833870,836650}Lassie, do you want to meet Dousho as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838600,840840}Who came this early morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841720,842690}- Colin?\N- Uh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842720,843970}John! Something bad happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844070,847130}Rory! Rory has troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847160,848440}- Eh?\N- What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853010,854030}- Oh?\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862850,864360}How many times should I tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864460,867040}I certainly turned off the fire before I slept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867090,869340}So how it burned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869370,870990}Well, Mr Rice…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871940,874690}This man worked hard to extinguish the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874830,876800}What is important is that the fire\Ndidn't reached the nearby houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876800,879770}What will you do if we can't control the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879900,883080}I also asked for help without any charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883110,885290}Don't think you will leave safely\Nafter you have caused the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885400,887080}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887640,888730}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888730,890830}Dad, you always do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:54.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891040,894220}You are very interested in your customers\Nto buy bread from our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894220,895690}This guy is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895720,896860}Don't joke with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896860,899920}I bake bread for the villagers only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900000,903270}I don't sell to men of this kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904140,905050}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905070,906050}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906130,909480}I don't know anything about bread,\Nbut it was hard to extinguish the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909760,910950}This means
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:14.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911020,914210}I must preserve my life and\Nthe life of the people of my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914700,917360}It is better to leave our village immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917800,919090}Do you have an objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921460,922760}I'll tell you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922830,924270}I didn't set fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924300,927030}No, no doubt it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927150,930890}I understand.  I don't like\Nto say this again though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930910,932010}Scum…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932010,934250}I know that, you don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936180,937390}You see? Definitely the reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941200,943010}I want to say only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944650,947960}I sell bowls and dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:53.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948220,953450}I travel to make people smile through\Nthe acrobatic games that Doucho loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953750,954630}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959060,960190}Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:01.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960870,961930}Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962030,963260}I have no other chioce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964220,965230}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965380,967470}Don't say "but" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967910,968830}Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969230,970750}The food was delicious, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973520,974760}It's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:19.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975000,979530}Well, the store owner wants me\Nto leave, so the village be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980570,982720}We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994730,996610}Rory… left…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998590,1001190}I don't know if the lamp\Nor wood caused th fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001330,1003940}It was close to my house and\Nit almost burned because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004030,1005140}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005410,1006280}A lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006810,1007830}Or wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007930,1008680}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010160,1011470}Hey Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011470,1013370}To the worst, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013940,1015740}Should I hit the door only?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019120,1020800}John, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:01.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020860,1021620}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021780,1024760}You say what?  But Mr. Rice is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024980,1026250}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026370,1028020}Mr Rice, I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:13.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028190,1033620}What? I must bake the bread late today\Nwith the oven already cooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033800,1034980}I'll go to bake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035050,1037000}Quick! He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037090,1038930}Sorry, Mr Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039570,1041250}What? I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041270,1042940}Not me, but Colin…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043800,1046110}Excuse me… this, sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046230,1048190}So I said, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050340,1051660}John, tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052000,1053030}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:35.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055090,1055680}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055880,1057200}Is this the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:37.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057230,1057940}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059200,1060420}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060530,1063830}The lamp and firewood were\Nextinguished at 11 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:44.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063850,1064480}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064700,1065280}Eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065410,1068950}This means that Colin woke up\Nand looked at the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068980,1071470}How come a child stays up until late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071490,1072150}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072600,1074930}I was trying to see the meteors…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075040,1076230}That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076380,1077920}Falling stars, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078030,1080680}If you talk loudly you will scare the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:01.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081170,1081850}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:05.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082020,1085270}Anyway, Mr. Rory turned off the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085340,1088180}And extinguished the fire with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088380,1089210}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:09.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089380,1089980}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:13.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090180,1093050}This means that wasn't the cause of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093230,1094030}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:18.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094580,1098190}If the cause of the fire is different\Nfrom that, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115830,1117690}Enough, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119290,1121110}Can't you go faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121200,1123140}I'm deaf, you're distracted in driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124340,1125140}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125270,1127750}What do I say to that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127770,1129250}You must apologize to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129610,1132850}I thought about the safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133080,1134590}If I say so…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:58.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134710,1138180}No matter what you say,\Nit's your fault anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139400,1142550}I was very impressed by Rory's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142910,1143550}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143810,1146370}I hope he stays in our village\Nand doesn't go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147180,1148090}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:13.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148730,1153340}I want to talk more with Mr. Rory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162870,1165260}Don't make this sad face, Duocho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165640,1168440}There are times when people should laugh at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168580,1170800}Hey, aren't you a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190220,1192460}What's up, Pace? Why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194090,1196420}Hey, get out of the way quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196500,1198470}The ship will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206510,1208620}Here it is! It's Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209070,1210430}Oh! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212220,1214350}Rory will cross the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214600,1216960}Damn, the engine hangs now…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221290,1222370}Rory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222440,1223990}Wait, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227950,1230190}You too, Dad! Run after the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233960,1235110}Hey Pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236480,1239860}I want to cross this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240330,1243850}In the next village\Nwe will see beautiful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251030,1252170}Hey come on, Pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257420,1258420}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258570,1259850}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260030,1261250}Oh Doucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:05.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264710,1265680}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265750,1267570}Rory, don't cross this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268280,1270490}My father, it's my father's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270730,1272210}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272580,1274280}Don't go on that road!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:33.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292810,1293580}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293790,1295630}This is because of these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:39.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296180,1299350}This means we will do\Nfun things there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303250,1304690}Yeah! Yeah!
